title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Local Legends - Find the manuals on  the MSFS 2020 website
description:
On of the things which is sometimes really challenging is finding the manuals of the aircrafts. In most cases they are put in a documentation folder inside the folder where the aircraft is installed. Asobo did now made a change for the Local Legends. For both aircrafts the manuals are now also available on their website. In this video we are going to looks where to find them.
